('416', '1', '2011-10-06 11:27:03', '2011-10-06 11:27:03', '<h3 class=\"entry-title\">PROJECT WIDE NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe in ground electricity is commencing, and weather permitting, should be completed end of October.\r\nDrainage pipes already on site, installation pending progress on electricity.\r\nAs we are getting close to finishing, the big 10 x 11 meter pool design is completed, and quotes are on their way. Commencing once the in ground electricity and drainage is completed.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">GENESIS TYPE C NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe 4 units Genesis type C is now almost closed.\r\nAll brickwork and wall finishing completed.\r\nWindows are ordered and to be installed shortly.\r\nThe curved roof will be installed as soon as the weather permits it.\r\nOnce fully closed, we can begin with ceilings, tiles and kitchen.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">COMPANY NEWS.</h3>\r\nWelcome to our brand new website.\r\nThis website has had a long time coming, and we expect to use this website as a hub for information for our customers. We will add information about current projects along with a resource of information about Thailand and Phuket.', 'October news for Genesis Rawai Project.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'news-october-genesis-rawai-project', '', '', '2012-01-23 07:19:44', '2012-01-23 07:19:44', '', '0', 'http://www.genesisvilla.com/?p=416', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
