('418', '1', '2011-12-10 11:47:59', '2011-12-10 11:47:59', '<h3 class=\"entry-title\">PROJECT WIDE NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe in ground electricity now just needs to be  hooked up with meters for each unit. We expect it to be complete in early January 2012\r\n\r\nWe started on the road within the project. Gravel and sand etc have been compressed to form the base of the road. The road itself is 15 centimeter thick reinforced cement.\r\n\r\nThe big pool is almost ready for tiles and pump and filter installation. All the plumbing, wiring and cement works are almost complete.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">GENESIS C NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe 4 units Genesis type C is now almost closed.\r\n\r\nBathroom countertops installed. Bathroom fixtures commencing.\r\n\r\nAircon units almost finished installation.\r\n\r\nKitchen cabinets have been installed, worktop and kitchen appliances will follow shortly.\r\n\r\nFinal remaining windows are being installed.\r\n\r\nThe jacuzzi’s for each unit are now ready for tiling.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">COMPANY NEWS.</h3>\r\nWelcome to our brand new website.\r\nThis website has had a long time coming, and we expect to use this website as a hub for information for our customers. We will add information about current projects along with a resource of information about Thailand and Phuket.', 'December news for Genesis Rawai Project.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'news-for-genesis-rawai-project', '', '', '2012-01-23 07:38:25', '2012-01-23 07:38:25', '', '0', 'http://www.genesisvilla.com/?p=418', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
('419', '1', '2012-01-06 11:51:35', '2012-01-06 11:51:35', '<h3 class=\"entry-title\">PROJECT WIDE NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe in ground electricity ( pipe works ) is completed. Suffered setbacks due to rain, but that was expected.\r\nNow commencing on running the actual cables. 50MW transformer installed, to supply the project with electricity.\r\nDrainage pipes completed.\r\nWe just started the works on the big pool.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">GENESIS C NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe 4 units Genesis type C is now almost closed.\r\nTiles are being installed.\r\nWalls are being painted.\r\nWindows are being installed.\r\nThe curved roof is finished.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">COMPANY NEWS.</h3>\r\nWelcome to our brand new website.\r\nThis website has had a long time coming, and we expect to use this website as a hub for information from our customers. We will add information about current projects along with a resource of information about Thailand and Phuket.', 'December news for Genesis Rawai Project.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'news-for-genesis-rawai-project-2', '', '', '2012-01-26 06:36:16', '2012-01-26 06:36:16', '', '0', 'http://www.genesisvilla.com/?p=419', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
