('423', '1', '2012-01-06 12:14:33', '2012-01-06 12:14:33', '<h3 class=\"entry-title\">PROJECT WIDE NEWS.</h3>\r\n\r\nThe in ground electricity is being hooked up with meters for each unit. We expect it to be complete by the end of the month.\r\nWe started on the road within the project. Gravel and sand etc have been compressed to form the base of the road. Once major works complete, we can cement the road surface.\r\nThe big pool is almost ready for tiles and pump and filter installation. All the plumbing, wiring and cement works are almost complete.\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">GENESIS C NEWS.</h3>\r\n\r\nThe 4 units Genesis type C is now almost closed.\r\nBathroom countertops installed. Bathroom fixtures commencing.\r\nAircon units almost finished installation.\r\nKitchen cabinets have been installed, worktop and kitchen appliances will follow shortly.\r\nFinal remaining windows are being installed.\r\nThe jacuzzi’s for each unit being built, almost ready for tiling.\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">COMPANY NEWS.</h3>\r\n\r\nWelcome to our brand new website.\r\nThis website has had a long time coming, and we expect to use this website as a hub for information from our customers. We will add information about current projects along with a resource of information about Thailand and Phuket.', 'news for Genesis Rawai Project.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '423', '', '', '2012-01-09 06:15:39', '2012-01-09 06:15:39', '', '0', 'http://www.genesisvilla.com/?p=423', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
