('439', '3', '2012-01-12 07:55:58', '2012-01-12 07:55:58', '<h3 class=\"entry-title\">PROJECT WIDE NEWS.</h3>\r\nElectricity is now up and running in all the units.\r\n\r\nThe perimeter wall and guard house is being completed. We expect the main gate to be installed late this month.\r\n\r\nThe big pool is being handed over at the end of the month. Completed tiling and installing equipment and filters.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">GENESIS C NEWS.</h3>\r\nThe 4 units Genesis type C are now almost finished.\r\n\r\nBathroom fixtures are nearly finished being installed.\r\n\r\nWalls are being painted with final coat of paint.\r\n\r\nKitchens complete.\r\n\r\nThe jacuzzi’s for each unit are near completion. Equipment  and tiling being done.\r\n<h3 class=\"entry-title\">COMPANY NEWS.</h3>\r\nWelcome to our brand new website.\r\nThis website has had a long time coming, and we expect to use this website as a hub for information for our customers. We will add information about current projects along with a resource of information about Thailand and Phuket.', 'January news for Genesis Rawai Project', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'january-news-for-genesis-rawai-project', '', '', '2012-01-23 07:56:46', '2012-01-23 07:56:46', '', '0', 'http://www.genesisvilla.com/?p=439', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
